extends ../layout

append layout-styles
  style.
    .card {
      transition: all .5s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: var(--bs-box-shadow);
      z-index: 2;
    }

block layout-content


  // Hero
  section.py-5.bg-white
    .container.text-center
      h1.fw-bold 2Lane Coffee ☕
      h2.fw-semibold.mt-2
        | A cozy café for good conversations

      p.lead.text-muted.mt-4.mb-0
        | Smartphone Garden is a small place where coffee, tea, frappes, and pastries are treated like plants in a garden.
        br
        | Each drink is a “little pot,” made to suit your pace and your story.

  // Story
  section.py-5.bg-light
    .container
      .row.align-items-center.g-4
        .col-12.col-lg-6
          h3.fw-semibold.mb-3 Our Café Story
          p.text-muted.mb-2
            | We started with a class assignment, then turned it into a real “café” — with a menu, stories, baristas, and regulars.
          p.text-muted.mb-2
            | Instead of selling phones, we thought it’d be friendlier to offer drinks you could “order” online.
          p.text-muted.mb-0
            | The interface, data, and experience are designed like an online café—simple, clear, and warmly welcoming.

        .col-12.col-lg-6
          .row.g-3
            .col-6
              .border.rounded-4.p-3.h-100.bg-white
                h4.h6.fw-semibold.mb-1 20+ drinks
                p.small.text-muted.mb-0
                  | Coffee, tea, frappes, desserts—something for every mood.
            .col-6
              .border.rounded-4.p-3.h-100.bg-white
                h4.h6.fw-semibold.mb-1 100% hand-crafted
                p.small.text-muted.mb-0
                  | Every item is hand-defined in our data, not just copied as templates.
            .col-6
              .border.rounded-4.p-3.h-100.bg-white
                h4.h6.fw-semibold.mb-1 Focused on experience
                p.small.text-muted.mb-0
                  | Filter drinks by category, tag, size, and price to find your favorite.
            .col-6
              .border.rounded-4.p-3.h-100.bg-white
                h4.h6.fw-semibold.mb-1 Learn & experiment
                p.small.text-muted.mb-0
                  | Both a class project and a playground for design & coding.

  // Cafe Inspiration
  section.py-5.bg-white
    .container
      .row.g-4
        .col-12.col-lg-4
            h3.h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 Why all?
            p.text-muted.mb-2
                | all means more than one path—it’s about being a place for both quiet moments alone and lively conversations with friends. We want our café to feel like a friendly street you walk down every day: simple, honest, and cozy.


        .col-12.col-lg-4
          h3.h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 What do we focus on?
          ul.list-unstyled.text-muted.mb-0
            li.mb-1
              span.fw-bold Smooth UI: 
              | built with Bootstrap 5, cards, modals, clear filtering.
            li.mb-1
              span.fw-bold True Data: 
              | Complete drinks menu with sizes, prices, tags.
            li.mb-1
              span.fw-bold Effortless UX: 
              | Ordering, filtering, and details are quick and simple.

        .col-12.col-lg-4
          h3.h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 If the café were real?
          p.text-muted.mb-2
            | Drop by any time, order a drink, and chill with your laptop for coding, studying, or simply relaxing.
          p.text-muted.mb-0
            | Even though our shop is online only, this website is the prototype for our dream.

